    dc:creator "Buck, William R.", "Cargill, D. Christine", "Latoszewski, Mikolaj", "Wolski, Grzegorz J." ;
    dc:date "2024" ;
    dc:title "Re-assessment of type material of Plagiothecium novae-seelandiae Broth. and descriptions of four new Plagiothecium taxa (Bryophyta, Plagiotheciaceae) from Australasia" ;
    bibo:endPage "117" ;
    bibo:journal "PhytoKeys" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2024-02-09" ;
    bibo:startPage "95" ;
    bibo:volume "238" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.114303.figure10>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.114303.figure11>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.114303.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.114303.figure9> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.114303.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Comparison of leaf shapes and dimensions of all described taxa A P. novae-seelandiae var. brotheri B P. novae-seelandiae var. novae-seelandiae C P. lamprostachys D P. semimortuum var. macquariense E P. semimortuum var. semimortuum F P. funale G P. cordatum (based on the types of the above-mentioned taxa, see Figs 3 - 9)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/982072" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.114303.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Distribution of the newly described taxa. Explanation: white triangles - P. semimortuum var. semimortuum; yellow circles - P. semimortuum var. macquariense; purple circles - P. novae-seelandiae var. brother; aquamarine squares - P. cordatum (Google Maps, accessed September 15, 2023)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/982073" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.114303.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Selected taxonomic features of P. lamprostachys A shape and dimensions of the leaf B leaf apex C cells from the middle part of the leaf D leaf basal cells (from the type of material of H. lamprostachys BM 000677528!, photo. G. J. Wolski, 01 August 2023)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/982065" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.114303.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Selected taxonomic features of Plagiothecium semimortuum var. macquariense A, B shape and dimensions of leaf C julaceous turf D dimensions and shape of cells from middle part of the leaf (from the type of P. semimortuum var. macquariense HO 610220, photo. G. J. Wolski, November 13, 2022)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/982071" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

